import { Box, Card, CardBody, Input, InputGroup, InputLeftElement } from "@chakra-ui/react"


export default function Busqueda() {
    return (
        <Box position="relative" marginX={30}>
            <Card h="61vh" w="51vw" minWidth="205px" minHeight="360px" borderRadius="35px">
                <CardBody >
                    <InputGroup>
                        <InputLeftElement>
                            <Search2Icon></Search2Icon>
                        </InputLeftElement>
                        <Input placeholder='Buscar canción' />
                    </InputGroup>
                </CardBody>
            </Card>
        </Box>
    );
}
